																<h3>About Hans Rosling</h3>
						<p>
							As a doctor and researcher, Hans Rosling identified a new paralytic disease induced by hunger in rural Africa. Now he looks at the bigger picture of social and economic development with his&hellip; <a target="_blank" class="external" href="/speakers/hans_rosling.html">Full bio and more links</a>						</p>
